sections.heading: Violation; penalty.Any person who violates any of the provisions of sections 71-1901 to 71-1906
sections.text: 01 shall be deemed guilty of a Class III misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1943, c. 154, § 5, p. 564;R.S.1943, § 71-1905;Laws 1945, c. 171, § 5, p. 550;Laws 1977, LB 39, § 163;Laws 1995, LB 451, § 5;Laws 2001, LB 20
